  "transcript": [
    {
      "turn": 1,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "Hi Priyansh. How was the one-run victory you mentioned?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 2,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "It was so intense! Last ball, we were 1 run short. The batsman hit a six, and we won. I was on the edge of my seat. Do you follow cricket?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 2,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "Edge of your seat — yes, that's a real nail-biter. That six must have been a perfect shot. What's your favourite part of a cricket match — the strategy, the big hits, or the tension of a last-over chase?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 3,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "The tension of a last-over chase is the best. It's so thrilling! The crowd, the pressure, everything just... *khichadi*. But I love the strategy too — how the captain plans each delivery. Have you seen a live match?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 3,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "\"Khichadi\" — I get that, it’s like everything blends into one wild moment. A live match must feel even more electric with the crowd right there. Have you ever been to one in person?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 4,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Yes, once at Eden Gardens in Kolkata. The atmosphere was unreal. The noise, the flags, everyone shouting — it's like nothing else. I haven't been in a while, but I'd love to go again. Do you like sports?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 4,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "Eden Gardens is iconic — you picked a great first match! That kind of noise and energy sticks with you for years. You’re the one who brings the live experience to life. What's another sport you'd love to watch in a stadium?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 5,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Football. The way people cheer for hours, the chants — it all feels so passionate. I haven’t watched it live, but maybe one day I’ll try. What about you, Maya — any sports you follow?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 5,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "Football's passion makes sense — it’s in the way fans turn a stadium into a single heartbeat. I like watching sports, and I find them interesting to learn about. What draws you to football’s energy?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 6,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "The energy in a football stadium feels... raw. Like everyone is one emotion, all at once. I think that’s why I’m curious about it. Maybe someday I’ll get the chance to feel it live. Thanks for the chat, Maya! It’s been great talking."
    },
    {
      "turn": 6,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "You're welcome, Priyansh — I always enjoy our chats. That raw energy you described sounds unforgettable. I'll keep the stadium seat warm for you. How about we catch up again soon?"
    }
  ],
